== 重要評價 ==
* <span>《記憶斷層</span>》可以和<span>[[凶心人|記憶拼圖]]</span><ref name="dvd1">Anthony Nield, [http://dvdtimes.co.uk/content.php?contentid=56673 "The I Inside" Review] {{Wayback|url=http://dvdtimes.co.uk/content.php?contentid=56673 |date=20050414164354 }}, ''DVD Times''</ref>'' 、''<span>[[連鎖蝶變|蝴蝶效應]]</span>,<ref name="cur1">[http://www.currentfilm.com/dvdreviews6/iinsidedvd.html "The I Inside" Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.currentfilm.com/dvdreviews6/iinsidedvd.html |date=20060508013718 }}, ''Current Film''</ref>'' <span>eXistenZ</span>,''<ref name="dvd1">Anthony Nield, [http://dvdtimes.co.uk/content.php?contentid=56673 "The I Inside" Review], ''DVD Times''</ref> 和 ''Jacob's Ladder''<ref name="fil1">Christopher Null, {{cite web |url=http://filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/60e74e041ca9cd6b8625626f0062219f/352020feadc3337c88256fc70061538a?OpenDocument |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-06-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130123054400/http://filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/60e74e041ca9cd6b8625626f0062219f/352020feadc3337c88256fc70061538a?OpenDocument |archivedate=2013-01-23 }}, ''Filmcritic.com''</ref> 等電影相比較。這些電影都以類似的元素為主題，並試著模糊化現實和奇幻之間的分界。

* The film has generally received luke-warm reviews from online critics. It holds a 33% rating on Rotten Tomatoes. Review sites have commended the film for a rather involving first two-thirds, with the mystery slowly being revealed layer by layer, drawing in the viewer. However, some critics found the ending a let down, calling it a "gotcha" gimmick<ref name="bey1">Nix, [http://www.beyondhollywood.com/reviews/theiinside.htm "The I Inside" Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beyondhollywood.com/reviews/theiinside.htm |date=20060212003609 }}, ''Beyond Hollywood''</ref> that causes "the past 70 or so minutes (to go) out the window".<ref name="bey1">Nix, [http://www.beyondhollywood.com/reviews/theiinside.htm "The I Inside" Review] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060212003609/http://www.beyondhollywood.com/reviews/theiinside.htm |date=2006-02-12 }}, ''Beyond Hollywood''</ref>

* Christopher Null of ''Filmcritic.com'' 提出了一個特別但是有趣的觀點： "The movie is based on a play with a much different title, one that actually gives away the surprise ending."<ref name="fil1">Christopher Null, {{cite web |url=http://filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/60e74e041ca9cd6b8625626f0062219f/352020feadc3337c88256fc70061538a?OpenDocument |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-06-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130123054400/http://filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/60e74e041ca9cd6b8625626f0062219f/352020feadc3337c88256fc70061538a?OpenDocument |archivedate=2013-01-23 }}, ''Filmcritic.com''</ref>

